Package: sqlmap
Version: 1.10.7
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: python, python-pip
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://sqlmap.org/
Description: Automatic SQL Injection and Database Takeover Tool
 sqlmap is an open source penetration testing tool that automates the process
 of detecting and exploiting SQL injection flaws and taking over of database
 servers. It comes with a powerful detection engine, many niche features for
 the ultimate penetration tester, and a broad range of switches including
 database fingerprinting, data fetching, accessing underlying file system,
 and executing commands on the operating system via out-of-band connections.
 Features:
 - Full support for multiple database systems
 - Six SQL injection techniques
 - Database and OS fingerprinting
 - Data extraction and file system access
 - Command execution and out-of-band connections
